2. Proposed Solution
Identify and define the metrics required to measure the success of...

3. Scope of the Project
This project will be completed in multiple phases.

  Phase 1 - Analysis
  The analysis of the metrics to measure the product.

  Phase 2 - Automation
  Automate an alarming alerting the customers when a metric is behind.

4. Design
Dashboard Features
  i. Ability to filter by customer and request date
  ii. Calculate request total
    a. By customer
    b. By date
    c. Filter by customer type and request type and aggregate it

5. Technical Architecture
The technical architecture will be combining multiple data sources via an ETL.

